        <briefdescription>
<para>Set the transmission timeout value. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>The transmission timeout controls the amount of time the Remote Provisioning Client models will wait for a response from the Server.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
